skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: train spotter
des:
This skill queries the @UP_Steam Twitter feed for information about Union Pacific steam locomotives, namely 844, 3985, and 4014. Both a summary of the latest information and searching for a specific locomotive is supported.

No account linking with Twitter is currently required.

This skill is not affiliated with Union Pacific Railroad.
